incidents.name: Network Performance Issues in North America

incident_updates.body:
On 2025-08-23 Cloudflare identified and resolved an issue that caused elevated latency for some end users in North America. This means some visitors to your site may have experienced slower loading times between approximately 17:15 and 23:15 UTC.

The issue was mitigated and resolved, and our team continues to monitor the situation to ensure stable performance. We sincerely apologize for any inconvenience this may have caused.
This incident is now resolved.

Queue is recovering and encoding jobs are completing. New uploads should be available normally, videos currently encoding should complete shortly. Team is continuing to investigate. Playback and live broadcasts were unaffected.
